_sText:
STILL FIRST MAP!

Due to demand, I retextured everything, added lighting, more spawnpoints, a little more detail, and added ambient noise. I also fixed a few minor bugs. Do not download v1 unless you want dev textures, fullbright, and seizures.

Fixed:
Fence area, harder for zombies
Bunker area, harder for zombies
Platform area, harder for humans
Ladder area, harder for humans
Fixed a few cheap spots

This map requires a lot of teamwork. Otherwise, you will get owned. There is no barricading at all. You will either be on top of something, or behind an already made barricade. Also, I've prevented stacking of humans by lowering the ceiling.
